HEADWORD: Briny
<hw>Brin"y</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Brine</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to brine, or to the sea;
partaking of the nature of brine; salt; <as>as, a <ex>briny</ex> taste;
the <ex>briny</ex> flood</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

